      "value": "<p><strong>Type&nbsp;</strong>disease (<span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListDiseases_ctl00_LabelName\">inhaled)</span>;&nbsp;<strong>Save&nbsp;</strong>Fortitude DC 12;</p>\n<p><strong>Onset&nbsp;</strong>3d6<span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListDiseases_ctl00_LabelName\">&nbsp;days</span>;&nbsp;<strong>Frequency&nbsp;</strong>1/day</p>\n<p><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>1d4 Con damage. Rolling a 1 on any Fortitude save to resist taking damage from fungal flu results in&nbsp;<a class=\"entity-link\" style=\"color: #ff6400; border: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background: none;\" draggable=\"false\" data-pack=\"pf1.conditions\" data-id=\"coxrkb6qUKBZvVxP\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">blindness</span></a>. The blindness persists - even resisting spells like&nbsp;<a class=\"entity-link\" style=\"color: #ff6400; border: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background: none;\" draggable=\"false\" data-pack=\"pf1.spells\" data-id=\"kundr7ekztiqml5t\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">remove blindness/deafness</span></a><a draggable=\"false\" data-pack=\"pf1.spells\" data-id=\"kundr7ekztiqml5t\">&nbsp;</a>- until the disease is cured.</p>\n<p><strong>Cure&nbsp;</strong>2 consecutive saves</p>",
